</odoo>

<!-- 
**Key Features:**

1. ✅ **Uses `<list>` not `<tree>`** - Odoo 18 compliant
2. **Complete workflow** - Buttons for Reserve → Start → Return → Invoice
3. **Color-coded rows** - Overdue (red), Reserved (blue), Returned (green)
4. **Status bar** - Visual workflow progress
5. **Ribbons** - "Overdue" and "Cancelled" ribbons
6. **Smart buttons** - Invoice count
7. **Financial totals** - Subtotals, late fees, damage fees
8. **Inline item editing** - Add/edit equipment directly
9. **Serial tracking** - View assigned serials per item
10. **Signatures & photos** - Pickup and return documentation
11. **Status history** - Complete audit trail
12. **Kanban board** - Drag-and-drop by state
13. **Chatter integration** - Activities and messages
14. **Pre-filtered views** - Draft, Ongoing, Overdue
-->
